    "text": [
        "The decision of buying either a new house or a flat is one of the most crucial in people\u2019s lives, showing their genuine interest to have this house bring them happiness and make them feel comfortable there. Because of this, a great deal of  people are curious about the history of the property they are about to buy. Let\u2019s dig deeper and figure out why.",
        "Firstly, once people decided to settle in a new house or a flat, it\u2019s worth checking some information about the wanted property in order to make sure it has good energy and nothing sorrowful happened there. Why? It a good question, though. Since loads of people are superstitious, they do believe that each place has either positive or negative energy so that people can easily feel it. If you settle in a place which feels awkward or doesn\u2019t make you feel safe and sound, it ought to bring you lowest points in your life.",
